IOS :

create the app : phonegap create hello com.example.hello HelloWorld
build the app : phonegap build ios
test the app : phonegap install ios
SI BESOIN :
sudo npm install -g ios-deploy
sudo npm install -g ios-sim

ANDROID :

1. install android sdk : http://developer.android.com/sdk/index.html
add to path : ADT\sdk\platform-tools
add to path : ADT\sdk\tools

2. install ant : cinst ant
add to path : apache-ant-1.9.3\bin
create androiv virtual device : "android" -> tools/avd

3. install java (jdk)
set java_home
add to path : %java_home%/bin

4. bootstrap the app
phonegap install android
phonegap run android
